1. Ubuntu package list to install
node (recomment to install manually)
freetds-common freetds-bin tdsodbc
unixodbc unixodbc-dev
libgmp-dev
mongodb

2. Npm list to install
bigint express mongojs odbc

3. Howto install da2-toople
git clone git://github.com/hyvaa/da2.git

4.Path configuration files
( Assume that 
	static ip of this server = 192.168.0.110
	static ip of doobune server = 192.168.0.100
	local DNS = toople.dc.local
)


/etc/freetds/freetds.conf
/etc/odbc.ini
/etc/odbcinst.ini

/etc/network/interfaces
/etc/bind/named.conf.options
/etc/bind/named.conf.local
/etc/bind/zones/dc.local.db
/etc/bind/zones/rev.0.168.192.in-addr.arpa

